---
title: Sizzling Ginger Shrimp with Katsu Sauce plus Scallion Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: If you’re like us, you’ve seen a lot of stir-fries in your day. But thanks to our aromatic shrimp marinade, scallion rice, a sprinkle of nutty sesame seeds, and a katsu sauce dipper, this one is bound to top them all. It cooks super quickly and brings a tour de force of tangy, sweet, and savory flavors that even the pickiest of eaters will love. Sounds like a win-win to us.
